to improve the stats of your heroes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043430/extras/9cb574db4ec23b32a4572b68c5f79fe8.poster.avif?t=1760778975\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043430/extras/9cb574db4ec23b32a4572b68c5f79fe8.webm?t=1760778975\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043430/extras/9cb574db4ec23b32a4572b68c5f79fe8.mp4?t=1760778975\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Please Wishlist - Coming Soon!</strong></p>",
